! Cross-Platform SCORM Forensics & Legacy Recovery
''Date:'' 2015–2022

! Context

Tier 1 global banking client across 5 countries. Found a SCORM API wrapper bug causing silent session termination, decompiled Flash SWFs to recover lost source files, and coordinated SCORM deployment fixes across Mexico, India, and the Philippines.

